title: Kimi no Iru Machi: Mousou 200-wa
original_name: 君のいる町 妄想 200 話
sinopse: Fantasy Chapter 200 is a series of special chapters released with the Kimi no Iru Machi anime Blu-ray/DVD limited edition sets. Original chapter 200 features Haruto and Yuzuki's first time, and the fantasy chapters are alternate versions featuring other female characters selected by a popularity poll.
